Note that the last few lines may appear out of order. This does not indicate failure in blocking, because the messages themselves are not synchronized.

The following example demonstrates the intended usage of this method:

public void DoSomething ()
{
	using (this.disposalHelper.AcquireHoldHandle())
	{
		//	Do something ...
	}
}

hcaExample.code:
